        "FGF7_FGF10": "KGF family secreted by DP \u2192 bind FGFR2b on matrix keratinocytes \u2192 proliferation and differentiation maintenance",
        "FGF2": "Basic FGF secreted by DP \u2192 anti-apoptotic for matrix cells \u2192 anagen prolongation",
        "VEGF": "Secreted by DP \u2192 binds VEGFR2 on endothelial cells \u2192 capillary formation \u2192 nutrient delivery to matrix"
