        "step_2": "AR-DHT complex translocates to nucleus \u2192 upregulates TGF-beta-2 gene transcription",
        "step_3": "TGF-beta-2 secreted into pericellular space \u2192 binds TGFBR2 on matrix keratinocytes \u2192 SMAD2/3 phosphorylation \u2192 growth arrest and apoptosis",
        "step_4": "AR-DHT also upregulates DKK-1 (Dickkopf-1) \u2192 Wnt receptor antagonist \u2192 blocks beta-catenin signalling \u2192 stem cell activation fails",
